---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import { fade, slide, ViewTransitions } from "astro:transitions";
---

<Layout
  title="About us - Dynamic Total Services"
  content="About us - Dynamic Total Services. - We understand the dynamic nature of the mining industry. With our flexible workforce management, you can easily adjust your staffing levels based on project demands, seasonal variations, or unforeseen events. We provide you with the agility to optimise productivity while minimising overhead costs."
>
  <main transition:name="main" transition:animate={slide({ duration: "0.4s" })}>
    <header class="m-auto py-8 bg-secondaryBg pt-16">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-center text-white">About Us</h1>
    </header>
    <div
      class="py-9 px-3 md:px-14 lg:px-32 min-h-[80vh] flex flex-col justify-center"
    >
      <div
        class="w-full border border-goldColor p-4 rounded-xl relative space-y-2"
      >
        <h3
          class="bg-primaryBg text-goldColor px-3 text-xs leading-7 font-bold md:text-xl absolute -top-4 left-1/4"
        >
          About Total Dynamic Services
        </h3>
        <p>
          At Dynamic Total Services, we strongly believe in unlocking potential,
          one opportunity at a time, empowering individuals to embrace their
          greatest and shape their future. We take pride in being a labour hire
          company that specialises in providing highly skilled candidates to
          work on mining sites across Western Australia. As a labour hire
          company for various organisations, we provide an external Human
          Resources service to outsource candidates that meet the criteria for
          the opportunity.
        </p>
        <p>
          We are deeply committed to offering a distinctive combination of
          specialised industry expertise, exceptional customer service, and a
          comprehensive candidate screening process. With a deep understanding
          of the mining and industrial sectors, we possess specialised industry
          knowledge that enables us to cater to the unique requirements and
          challenges of these industries. Our team of experienced professionals
          brings valuable insights and expertise, ensuring we can effectively
          match skilled workers to specific job roles and projects.
        </p>
        <p>
          In addition to our labour hire services, Dynamic Total Services also
          offers premium rubber lining services. Our new workshop in Bunbury is
          equipped with state-of-the-art facilities and staffed by experienced
          rubber liners who deliver top-quality workmanship. We provide a range
          of rubber lining solutions designed to protect equipment, enhance
          durability, and improve performance in harsh industrial environments.
          Our rubber lining services complement our labour hire offerings,
          providing a comprehensive solution to meet the diverse needs of our
          clients in the mining and industrial sectors.
        </p>
      </div>
